{"tid":2176816,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"戴「豬嘴」諷京空氣污染被刪除","createTime":"2020-08-27T10:10:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T10:10:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d46103582d5e0efe292ec0ff02049e5bafa3e995","tid":2176816,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:10:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200827/QYNRN6DM5ZEJ3E3DRWAJP6TCOQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200827%2FQYNRN6DM5ZEJ3E3DRWAJP6TCOQ%2F&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97Zvpk6arsW1wokO1n9cqNe5yO8o%3D&h=b80c131c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200827%2FQYNRN6DM5ZEJ3E3DRWAJP6TCOQ%2F&h=0431c90d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200827/QYNRN6DM5ZEJ3E3DRWAJP6TCOQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n戴「豬嘴」諷京空氣污染被刪除<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Sumy5MkD4Eky2D2iXl-bpUDEzWQ=/1215x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/F3EZTKLDWNGTFFBVNZVF7VJUD4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSumy5MkD4Eky2D2iXl-bpUDEzWQ%3D%2F1215x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FF3EZTKLDWNGTFFBVNZVF7VJUD4.jpg&h=b8df008d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■新版刪走一幅畫有國際跑手戴「豬嘴」參與北京國際馬拉松的漫畫。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本報發現多本初中通識及生社科教科書被「河蟹」後，多處涉及中國政府爭議的內容被大幅刪除，包括刪去推廣普通話令方言消失的練習，一幅國際跑手戴「豬嘴」參與北京國際馬拉松，諷刺中國空氣污染的漫畫亦被刪去。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n刪走推廣普通話消滅方言<br />\n<br />\n雅集出版社的《雅集初中基礎議題》「現代中國」單元中，舊版題為「推廣普通話」的練習中，有一幅漫畫以「推土車」比喻中國推廣普通話，及以「倒塌房屋」比喻中國方言，象徵中國政府推廣普通話後令方言消失；惟修訂後。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n同一單元，在「管治挑戰」中，舊版列出「道德水平下滑」、「社會矛盾加劇」及亦同樣刪走。"}]}